<template>
  <a-config-provider :locale="locale">
    <!-- <App /> -->
    <router-view/>
  </a-config-provider>
</template>

<script>
  import zhCN from 'ant-design-vue/es/locale/zh_CN';
  import dayjs from 'dayjs';
  import 'dayjs/locale/zh-cn';
  dayjs.locale('zh-cn');

  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        locale: zhCN,
      };
    },
  };
</script>
